FormFieldDefinition.title: Contas Financeiras
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT HANDLE FROM CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS WHERE HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO) AND ( ( EMITEDEMONSTRATIVO = 'F' AND DFCORIGEM = 2 ) OR ( TIPOPLANO = 1 ) )

FormFieldDefinition.title: Subcontas Correlatas
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT HANDLE FROM CT_CONTASGERENCIAIS WHERE SUBCONTACORRELATA IS NULL AND (METODOCONTROLESUBCONTA IN (SELECT HANDLE FROM EDCF_METODOSCONTROLE WHERE EDCF_METODOSCONTROLE.CODIGO IN ('A', 'B', 'F', 'G')) OR HANDLE IN (SELECT CT_SUBCONTASGERENCIAIS.CONTAGERENCIAL FROM CT_SUBCONTASGERENCIAIS WHERE CT_SUBCONTASGERENCIAIS.CONTAGERENCIAL = CT_CONTASGERENCIAIS.HANDLE)) AND HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO)

FormFieldDefinition.title: Contas Calculadas
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT FN_PARAMETROS.HANDLE FROM FN_PARAMETROS, CT_CONTASGERENCIAIS, CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS WHERE FN_PARAMETROS.EMPRESA = @EMPRESA AND FN_PARAMETROS.ORCAMENTOPUBLICO <> 'S' AND CT_CONTASGERENCIAIS.HANDLE = @CAMPO(HANDLE) AND CT_CONTASGERENCIAIS.ORCAMENTO <> 'C' AND CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO) AND CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO = 1

FormFieldDefinition.title: Contas Cont√°beis
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE FROM CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS LEFT JOIN ED_PLANOVERSOES ON CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.PLANOCONTAS = ED_PLANOVERSOES.HANDLE WHERE CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO) AND NOT (CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.EMITEDEMONSTRATIVO = 'F' AND CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.DFCORIGEM = 2) AND (((CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO = 3) AND (ED_PLANOVERSOES.PLANOCONTABIL IS NOT NULL)) OR (CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO <> 3))

FormFieldDefinition.title: Contas Gerenciais
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE FROM CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS LEFT JOIN ED_PLANOVERSOES ON CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.PLANOCONTAS = ED_PLANOVERSOES.HANDLE WHERE CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO) AND (((CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO = 3) AND (ED_PLANOVERSOES.PLANOGERENCIAL IS NOT NULL)) OR (CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO <> 3))

FormFieldDefinition.title: Prazos de realiza√ß√£o
FormFieldDefinition.Expression: SELECT FN_PARAMETROS.HANDLE FROM FN_PARAMETROS JOIN CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS ON CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.EMPRESA = FN_PARAMETROS.EMPRESA WHERE FN_PARAMETROS.EMPRESA = @EMPRESA AND CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.HANDLE = @CAMPO(PLANO) AND FN_PARAMETROS.ORCAMENTOPUBLICO <> 'S' AND CT_PLANOSGERENCIAIS.TIPOPLANO = 1
